{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"John Hockenberry: It's great to be here with you, Tom."},{"time":2000,"text":"And I want to start with a question"},{"time":4000,"text":"that has just been consuming me"},{"time":6000,"text":"since I first became familiar with your work."},{"time":9000,"text":"In you work there's always this kind of hybrid quality"},{"time":12000,"text":"of a natural force"},{"time":15000,"text":"in some sort of interplay with creative force."},{"time":18000,"text":"Are they ever in equilibrium"},{"time":20000,"text":"in the way that you see your work?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"Tom Shannon: Yeah, the subject matter that I'm looking for,"},{"time":25000,"text":"it's usually to solve a question."},{"time":27000,"text":"I had the question popped into my head:"},{"time":29000,"text":"What does the cone that connects the sun and the Earth look like"},{"time":33000,"text":"if you could connect the two spheres?"},{"time":36000,"text":"And in proportion, what would the size of the sphere"},{"time":39000,"text":"and the length, and what would the taper be to the Earth?"},{"time":43000,"text":"And so I went about and made that sculpture,"},{"time":46000,"text":"turning it out of solid bronze."},{"time":49000,"text":"And I did one that was about 35 feet long."},{"time":52000,"text":"The sun end was about four inches in diameter,"},{"time":55000,"text":"and then it tapered over about 35 feet"},{"time":58000,"text":"to about a millimeter at the Earth end."},{"time":61000,"text":"And so for me, it was really exciting"},{"time":63000,"text":"just to see what it looks like"},{"time":66000,"text":"if you could step outside and into a larger context,"},{"time":69000,"text":"as though you were an astronaut,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and see these two things as an object,"},{"time":74000,"text":"because they are so intimately bound,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and one is meaningless without the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"JH: Is there a relief"},{"time":82000,"text":"in playing with these forces?"},{"time":84000,"text":"And I'm wondering how much of a sense of discovery there is"},{"time":87000,"text":"in playing with these forces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"TS: Well, like the magnetically levitated objects --"},{"time":92000,"text":"like that silver one there,"},{"time":94000,"text":"that was the result"},{"time":96000,"text":"of hundreds of experiments with magnets,"},{"time":98000,"text":"trying to find a way to make something float"},{"time":101000,"text":"with the least possible connection to the ground."},{"time":104000,"text":"So I got it down to just one tether"},{"time":107000,"text":"to be able to support that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"JH: Now is this electromagnetic here, or are these static?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"TS: Those are permanent magnets, yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"JH: Because if the power went out, there would just be a big noise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117000,"text":"TS: Yeah."},{"time":119000,"text":"It's really unsatisfactory having plug-in art."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"JH: I agree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"TS: The magnetic works"},{"time":127000,"text":"are a combination of gravity and magnetism,"},{"time":130000,"text":"so it's a kind of mixture of these ambient forces"},{"time":133000,"text":"that influence everything."},{"time":135000,"text":"The sun has a tremendous field"},{"time":137000,"text":"that extends way beyond the planets"},{"time":139000,"text":"and the Earth's magnetic field protects us from the sun."},{"time":142000,"text":"So there's this huge"},{"time":144000,"text":"invisible shape structures"},{"time":147000,"text":"that magnetism takes in the universe."},{"time":150000,"text":"But with the pendulum,"},{"time":153000,"text":"it allows me to manifest"},{"time":156000,"text":"these invisible forces"},{"time":158000,"text":"that are holding the magnets up."},{"time":160000,"text":"My sculptures"},{"time":162000,"text":"are normally very simplified."},{"time":165000,"text":"I try to refine them down"},{"time":167000,"text":"to very simple forms."},{"time":169000,"text":"But the paintings become very complex,"},{"time":171000,"text":"because I think the fields"},{"time":173000,"text":"that are supporting them,"},{"time":175000,"text":"they're billowing, and they're interpenetrating,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and they're interference patterns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"JH: And they're non-deterministic."},{"time":182000,"text":"I mean, you don't know necessarily where you're headed when you begin,"},{"time":185000,"text":"even though the forces can be calculated."},{"time":188000,"text":"So the evolution of this --"},{"time":190000,"text":"I gather this isn't your first pendulum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"TS: No. (JH: No.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194000,"text":"TS: The first one I did was in the late 70's,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and I just had a simple cone"},{"time":199000,"text":"with a spigot at the bottom of it."},{"time":202000,"text":"I threw it into an orbit,"},{"time":204000,"text":"and it only had one color,"},{"time":206000,"text":"and when it got to the center, the paint kept running out,"},{"time":209000,"text":"so I had to run in there,"},{"time":211000,"text":"didn't have any control over the spigot remotely."},{"time":214000,"text":"So that told me right away: I need a remote control device."},{"time":217000,"text":"But then I started dreaming of having six colors."},{"time":220000,"text":"I sort of think about it as the DNA --"},{"time":223000,"text":"these colors, the red, blue, yellow,"},{"time":225000,"text":"the primary colors and white and black."},{"time":228000,"text":"And if you put them together in different combinations --"},{"time":230000,"text":"just like printing in a sense,"},{"time":232000,"text":"like how a magazine color is printed --"},{"time":234000,"text":"and put them under certain forces,"},{"time":237000,"text":"which is orbiting them"},{"time":239000,"text":"or passing them back and forth"},{"time":241000,"text":"or drawing with them,"},{"time":243000,"text":"these amazing things started appearing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"JH: It looks like we're loaded for bear here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"TS: Yeah, well let's put a couple of canvases."},{"time":250000,"text":"I'll ask a couple of my sons"},{"time":252000,"text":"to set up the canvases here."},{"time":256000,"text":"I want to just say --"},{"time":258000,"text":"so this is Jack, Nick and Louie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":260000,"text":"JH: Thanks guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263000,"text":"TS: So here are the --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"JH: All right, I'll get out of the way here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"TS: I'm just going to throw this into an orbit"},{"time":270000,"text":"and see if I can paint everybody's shoes in the front."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286000,"text":"JH: Whoa. That is ..."},{"time":291000,"text":"ooh, nice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295000,"text":"TS: So something like this."},{"time":297000,"text":"I'm doing this as a demo,"},{"time":299000,"text":"and it's more playful,"},{"time":302000,"text":"but inevitably,"},{"time":304000,"text":"all of this can be used."},{"time":307000,"text":"I can redeem this painting,"},{"time":309000,"text":"just continuing on,"},{"time":311000,"text":"doing layers upon layers."},{"time":313000,"text":"And I keep it around for a couple of weeks,"},{"time":315000,"text":"and I'm contemplating it,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and I'll do another session with it"},{"time":320000,"text":"and bring it up to another level,"},{"time":323000,"text":"where all of this"},{"time":325000,"text":"becomes the background, the depth of it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"JH: That's fantastic."},{"time":333000,"text":"So the valves at the bottom of those tubes there"},{"time":336000,"text":"are like radio-controlled airplane valves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"TS: Yes, they're servos with cams"},{"time":342000,"text":"that pinch these rubber tubes."},{"time":344000,"text":"And they can pinch them very tight and stop it,"},{"time":346000,"text":"or you can have them wide open."},{"time":348000,"text":"And all of the colors"},{"time":350000,"text":"come out one central port"},{"time":352000,"text":"at the bottom."},{"time":354000,"text":"You can always be changing colors, put aluminum paint,"},{"time":357000,"text":"or I could put anything into this."},{"time":359000,"text":"It could be tomato sauce,"},{"time":362000,"text":"or anything could be dispensed --"},{"time":365000,"text":"sand, powders or anything like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"JH: So many forces there."},{"time":370000,"text":"You've got gravity, you've got the centrifugal force,"},{"time":372000,"text":"you've got the fluid dynamics."},{"time":378000,"text":"Each of these beautiful paintings,"},{"time":381000,"text":"are they images in and of themselves,"},{"time":384000,"text":"or are they records"},{"time":386000,"text":"of a physical event"},{"time":388000,"text":"called the pendulum approaching the canvas?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"TS: Well, this painting here,"},{"time":393000,"text":"I wanted to do something very simple,"},{"time":395000,"text":"a simple, iconic image"},{"time":397000,"text":"of two ripples interfering."},{"time":400000,"text":"So the one on the right was done first,"},{"time":402000,"text":"and then the one on the left"},{"time":404000,"text":"was done over it."},{"time":406000,"text":"And then I left gaps"},{"time":408000,"text":"so you could see the one that was done before."},{"time":410000,"text":"And then when I did the second one,"},{"time":412000,"text":"it really disturbed the piece --"},{"time":414000,"text":"these big blue lines"},{"time":416000,"text":"crashing through the center of it --"},{"time":418000,"text":"and so it created a kind of tension and an overlap."},{"time":421000,"text":"There are lines in front of the one on the right,"},{"time":425000,"text":"and there are lines behind the one on the left,"},{"time":428000,"text":"and so it takes it into different planes."},{"time":432000,"text":"What it's also about,"},{"time":434000,"text":"just the little events,"},{"time":437000,"text":"the events of the interpenetration of --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"JH: Two stars, or --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"TS: Two things that happened --"},{"time":444000,"text":"there's an interference pattern, and then a third thing happens."},{"time":447000,"text":"There are shapes that come about"},{"time":449000,"text":"just by the marriage"},{"time":451000,"text":"of two events that are happening,"},{"time":453000,"text":"and I'm very interested in that."},{"time":456000,"text":"Like the occurrence of moire patterns."},{"time":459000,"text":"Like this green one,"},{"time":461000,"text":"this is a painting I did about 10 years ago,"},{"time":464000,"text":"but it has some --"},{"time":466000,"text":"see, in the upper third --"},{"time":468000,"text":"there are these moires and interference patterns"},{"time":471000,"text":"that are radio kind of imagery."},{"time":473000,"text":"And that's something that in painting"},{"time":475000,"text":"I've never seen done."},{"time":477000,"text":"I've never seen a representation"},{"time":479000,"text":"of a kind of radio interference patterns,"},{"time":482000,"text":"which are so ubiquitous"},{"time":485000,"text":"and such an important part of our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":488000,"text":"JH: Is that a literal part of the image,"},{"time":490000,"text":"or is my eye making that interference pattern --"},{"time":493000,"text":"is my eye completing that interference pattern?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"TS: It is the paint actually,"},{"time":497000,"text":"makes it real."},{"time":499000,"text":"It's really manifested there."},{"time":501000,"text":"If I throw a very concentric circle,"},{"time":504000,"text":"or concentric ellipse,"},{"time":506000,"text":"it just dutifully makes"},{"time":508000,"text":"these evenly spaced lines,"},{"time":510000,"text":"which get closer and closer together,"},{"time":513000,"text":"which describes how gravity works."},{"time":515000,"text":"There's something very appealing"},{"time":517000,"text":"about the exactitude of science"},{"time":519000,"text":"that I really enjoy."},{"time":521000,"text":"And I love the shapes that I see"},{"time":524000,"text":"in scientific observations"},{"time":527000,"text":"and apparatus,"},{"time":529000,"text":"especially astronomical forms"},{"time":532000,"text":"and the idea of the vastness of it,"},{"time":534000,"text":"the scale,"},{"time":536000,"text":"is very interesting to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538000,"text":"My focus in recent years"},{"time":541000,"text":"has kind of shifted more toward biology."},{"time":544000,"text":"Some of these paintings, when you look at them very close,"},{"time":547000,"text":"odd things appear"},{"time":549000,"text":"that really look like horses or birds"},{"time":552000,"text":"or crocodiles, elephants."},{"time":555000,"text":"There are lots of things that appear."},{"time":557000,"text":"When you look into it, it's sort of like looking at cloud patterns,"},{"time":560000,"text":"but sometimes they're very modeled and highly rendered."},{"time":563000,"text":"And then there are all these forms"},{"time":565000,"text":"that we don't know what they are,"},{"time":567000,"text":"but they're equally well-resolved"},{"time":569000,"text":"and complex."},{"time":571000,"text":"So I think, conceivably, those could be predictive."},{"time":574000,"text":"Because since it has the ability"},{"time":576000,"text":"to make forms"},{"time":578000,"text":"that look like forms that we're familiar with"},{"time":580000,"text":"in biology,"},{"time":582000,"text":"it's also making other forms that we're not familiar with."},{"time":585000,"text":"And maybe it's the kind of forms"},{"time":587000,"text":"we'll discover underneath the surface of Mars,"},{"time":589000,"text":"where there are probably lakes"},{"time":591000,"text":"with fish swimming under the surface."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"JH: Oh, let's hope so. Oh, my God, let's."},{"time":595000,"text":"Oh, please, yes. Oh, I'm so there."},{"time":598000,"text":"You know, it seems"},{"time":601000,"text":"at this stage in your life,"},{"time":603000,"text":"you also very personally"},{"time":605000,"text":"are in this state of confrontation"},{"time":608000,"text":"with a sort of dissonant --"},{"time":611000,"text":"I suppose it's an electromagnetic force"},{"time":613000,"text":"that somehow governs your Parkinson's"},{"time":615000,"text":"and this creative force"},{"time":617000,"text":"that is both the artist"},{"time":620000,"text":"who is in the here and now"},{"time":622000,"text":"and this sort of arc of your whole life."},{"time":624000,"text":"Is that relevant to your work?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":627000,"text":"TS: As it turns out,"},{"time":629000,"text":"this device kind of comes in handy,"},{"time":631000,"text":"because I don't have to have"},{"time":633000,"text":"the fine motor skills to do,"},{"time":635000,"text":"that I can operate slides,"},{"time":637000,"text":"which is more of a mental process."},{"time":639000,"text":"I'm looking at it and making decisions:"},{"time":642000,"text":"It needs more red, it needs more blue,"},{"time":644000,"text":"it needs a different shape."},{"time":646000,"text":"And so I make these creative decisions"},{"time":649000,"text":"and can execute them"},{"time":652000,"text":"in a much, much simpler way."},{"time":654000,"text":"I mean, I've got the symptoms."},{"time":657000,"text":"I guess Parkinson's kind of creeps up over the years,"},{"time":660000,"text":"but at a certain point you start seeing the symptoms."},{"time":663000,"text":"In my case,"},{"time":665000,"text":"my left hand has a significant tremor"},{"time":668000,"text":"and my left leg also."},{"time":671000,"text":"I'm left-handed, and so I draw."},{"time":674000,"text":"All my creations"},{"time":676000,"text":"really start on small drawings,"},{"time":679000,"text":"which I have thousands of,"},{"time":681000,"text":"and it's my way of just thinking."},{"time":683000,"text":"I draw with a simple pencil,"},{"time":686000,"text":"and at first, the Parkinson's"},{"time":688000,"text":"was really upsetting,"},{"time":690000,"text":"because I couldn't get the pencil to stand still."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694000,"text":"JH: So you're not a gatekeeper for these forces."},{"time":697000,"text":"You don't think of yourself as the master of these forces."},{"time":700000,"text":"You think of yourself as the servant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703000,"text":"TS: Nature is -- well, it's a godsend."},{"time":706000,"text":"It just has so much in it."},{"time":709000,"text":"And I think nature"},{"time":711000,"text":"wants to express itself"},{"time":713000,"text":"in the sense that we are nature,"},{"time":715000,"text":"humans are of the universe."},{"time":718000,"text":"The universe is in our mind,"},{"time":720000,"text":"and our minds are in the universe."},{"time":722000,"text":"And we are expressions"},{"time":724000,"text":"of the universe, basically."},{"time":726000,"text":"As humans,"},{"time":728000,"text":"ultimately being part of the universe,"},{"time":731000,"text":"we're kind of the spokespeople"},{"time":733000,"text":"or the observer part"},{"time":735000,"text":"of the constituency"},{"time":738000,"text":"of the universe."},{"time":740000,"text":"And to interface with it,"},{"time":742000,"text":"with a device that lets these forces"},{"time":745000,"text":"that are everywhere"},{"time":747000,"text":"act and show what they can do,"},{"time":749000,"text":"giving them pigment and paint just like an artist,"},{"time":752000,"text":"it's a good ally."},{"time":755000,"text":"It's a terrific studio assistant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757000,"text":"JH: Well, I love the idea"},{"time":759000,"text":"that somewhere within this idea"},{"time":761000,"text":"of fine motion and control"},{"time":764000,"text":"with the traditional skills"},{"time":766000,"text":"that you have with your hand,"},{"time":768000,"text":"some sort of more elemental force gets revealed,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and that's the beauty here."},{"time":772000,"text":"Tom, thank you so much. It's been really, really great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775000,"text":"TS: Thank you, John."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}